quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  38,62,"Waqaloo ma lana lanara rijalan kunna naAAudduhum mina al-ashrar"
  38,63,"Attakhathnahum sikhriyyan am zaghatAAanhumu al-absar"
  38,64,"Inna thalika lahaqqun takhasumuahli annar"
  38,65,"Qul innama ana munthirunwama min ilahin illa Allahu alwahidualqahhar"
  38,66,"Rabbu assamawati wal-ardiwama baynahuma alAAazeezu alghaffar"
  38,67,"Qul huwa nabaon AAatheem"
  38,68,"Antum AAanhu muAAridoon"
  38,69,"Ma kana liya min AAilmin bilmala-ial-aAAla ith yakhtasimoon"
  38,70,"In yooha ilayya illa annamaana natheerun mubeen"
  38,71,"Ith qala rabbuka lilmala-ikatiinnee khaliqun basharan min teen"
  38,72,"Fa-itha sawwaytuhu wanafakhtu feehimin roohee faqaAAoo lahu sajideen"
  38,73,"Fasajada almala-ikatu kulluhumajmaAAoon"
  38,74,"Illa ibleesa istakbara wakanamina alkafireen"
  38,75,"Qala ya ibleesu mamanaAAaka an tasjuda lima khalaqtu biyadayya astakbarta amkunta mina alAAaleen"
  38,76,"Qala ana khayrun minhukhalaqtanee min narin wakhalaqtahu min teen"
  38,77,"Qala fakhruj minhafa-innaka rajeem"
  38,78,"Wa-inna AAalayka laAAnatee ila yawmiaddeen"
  38,79,"Qala rabbi faanthirneeila yawmi yubAAathoon"
  38,80,"Qala fa-innaka mina almunthareen"
  38,81,"Ila yawmi alwaqti almaAAloom"
  38,82,"Qala fabiAAizzatika laoghwiyannahumajmaAAeen"
  38,83,"Illa AAibadaka minhumualmukhlaseen"
